    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute gem! It's in such incredible shape that it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've pampered this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents\u2014just pure perfection inside and out. I'm looking for a quick sale to a good home, so I've priced it to fly! Come take a look and see for yourself, you're going to love it!",
