    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since the day it was first purchased. The exterior boasts its original, deep-gloss factory paint with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather seats are supple and free of creases, the carpets are pristine under original floor mats, and it still retains that distinctive new-car scent. Mechanically, it is flawless. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete binder of records to prove its pedigree. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did when it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
