      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that retains its original integrity. Meticulously serviced and preserved, it offers a rare combination of mechanical perfection and aesthetic distinction. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than the superlative.",
      "price": 48500.0,
