      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled off the lot yesterday. I\u2019ve babied it from day one, so you won't find a single scratch or blemish anywhere. It drives like a cloud and looks even better in person. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make the next owner so happy. Come swing by and see it for yourself\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
