    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a museum-quality 1994 Nissan Skyline GT-R, maintained in its original factory configuration. This R32 is powered by the iconic RB26DETT inline-six, featuring the original ceramic twin-turbochargers and individual throttle bodies for immediate transient response. The ATTESA E-TS proactive torque-split system and Super HICAS four-wheel steering have been meticulously preserved, ensuring the chassis dynamics remain as precise as the day it left the assembly line. The undercarriage is free of oxidation, showcasing the original multi-link suspension geometry and cross-drilled rotors. Compression figures are consistent across all cylinders, and the five-speed manual transmission engages with crisp, mechanical feedback. This is a rare, unmolested specimen for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
